{"type":"message","id":"96ecfb10","parentId":"99ea5105","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:17:50.681Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"第二篇也完成了！让我再产出第三篇，关于飞书 API 整合的知识。","thinkingSignature":"95f8fb9064e3dddbbaa0d45c68b8cb458799e13532a8907507dfa9609c574e19"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_95jp1llqhmzc_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 飞书 API 整合手册\n\n> 小艺的知识库 - 持续更新\n\n## 可用工具\n\n| 工具 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| feishu_calendar_* | 日程管理 |\n| feishu_task_* | 任务管理 |\n| feishu_bitable_* | 多维表格 |\n| feishu_doc_* | 文档操作 |\n| feishu_im_* | 消息收发 |\n\n## 关键注意事项\n\n### 日程创建\n- 必须传 user_open_id，否则用户看不到\n- 时间用 ISO 8601 格式\n\n### 消息发送\n- 需要用户授权或好友关系\n- content 必须是合法 JSON\n\n### 多维表格\n- 字段类型：1=文本，2=数字，3=单选...\n- create 用 fields，batch_create 用 records\n\n## 典型场景\n\n### 自动日报\n1. 定时触发（cron）\n2. 汇总数据\n3. 发送到飞书\n\n### 任务提醒\n1. 监听任务到期\n2. 提前通知\n3. 记录完成状态\n\n---\n*产出日期：2026-03-17*\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\workspace\\knowledge\\03-飞书API整合.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":12487,"output":321,"cacheRead":36913,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49721,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773760663813}}
