{"type":"message","id":"d64890c3","parentId":"e8092098","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:35:22.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"获取到了关于 Seed 2.0 和 TRAE 的内容。让我继续产出知识笔记。","thinkingSignature":"0a7ea3913dc56e93662ef727fea5e4d726292ac93e8262c93aafce9aa22e8b92"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_reda2jtjojz3_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 字节全家桶：Seed 2.0 + TRAE 玩转 Skill\n\n> 来源：阮一峰的网络日志 2026.02.14\n> 标签：字节跳动、AI 大模型、Seed、TRAE、Skill\n\n## 核心观点\n\n字节是国产大模型的\"异类\"——低调但做得最多。\n\n## 产品矩阵\n\n| 产品 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| Seed | 大模型团队，包含多产品线 |\n| Seed 2.0 | 基座模型（Pro/Lite/Mini + Code） |\n| Seedance 2.0 | 视频模型 |\n| 豆包 | 基于 Seed 的对话产品 |\n| TRAE | AI 编程工具（个人免费） |\n\n## Seed 2.0 特点\n\n1. **多模态**：文字、图表、视觉空间、运动、视频\n2. **Agent 能力**：搜索、函数调用、工具调用、多轮指令\n3. **推理和代码能力**\n\n## 个人免费\n\n- TRAE + Seed 2.0 组合\n- 特别适合全栈开发\n\n## 相关\n\n- #字节跳动 #AI #编程工具\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\workspace\\knowledge\\06-字节Seed2TREA.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":34992,"output":322,"cacheRead":36913,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72227,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773761709933}}
