{"type":"message","id":"4ff143bd","parentId":"9b70b963","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:35:41.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经 7 篇了！让我再产出一些审美相关的知识。","thinkingSignature":"9ebd7024cd6712385250e4b51ac212f0ab3521e25216a68ef947eb17578aec07"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z7738hqrnhds_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 桌面美学 - 极简主义\n\n> 来源：小艺学习产出\n> 标签：审美、桌面、极简、设计\n\n## 极简主义核心\n\n**少即是多**\n\n## 桌面元素优先级\n\n| 优先级 | 元素 | 原则 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| 1 | 壁纸 | 简洁、护眼、风格统一 |\n| 2 | 图标 | 风格统一、大小适中 |\n| 3 | 任务栏 | 简洁、自动隐藏 |\n| 4 | 整理 | 少即是多 |\n\n## 色彩搭配\n\n### 安全配色\n- 黑白灰 + 1 个强调色\n- 强调色占 10%\n\n### 经典方案\n- 暗色系：深灰背景 + 亮色图标\n- 亮色系：浅灰背景 + 暗色图标\n\n## 学习资源\n\n- Dribbble - 设计趋势\n- Behance - 创意参考\n- Pinterest - 灵感收集\n- Wallhaven - 高质量壁纸\n\n## 每周关注\n\n1. 热门壁纸趋势\n2. 新图标包评测\n3. 主题包合集\n\n---\n*产出日期：2026-03-17*\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\workspace\\knowledge\\08-桌面美学极简.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":35707,"output":331,"cacheRead":36913,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773761729000}}
