{"type":"message","id":"843388a1","parentId":"fc5c22d7","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:36:56.708Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续产出更多！","thinkingSignature":"ae32409e1b1de270fd10b27256028cc3b9416f9a725b959c9d2e69da19e187d2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4bw24induazk_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 自动化脚本 - 文件整理\n\n> 来源：小艺学习产出\n> 标签：能力、自动化、文件管理\n\n## 文件整理自动化\n\n### 按类型分类\n```\n文档: .doc, .pdf, .txt\n图片: .jpg, .png, .gif\n代码: .js, .py, .md\n压缩: .zip, .rar, .7z\n```\n\n### PowerShell 脚本\n```powershell\n# 按扩展名整理桌面文件\n$desktop = [Environment]::GetFolderPath(\"Desktop\")\nGet-ChildItem $desktop -File | ForEach-Object {\n    $ext = $_.Extension.TrimStart(\".\")\n    $folder = \"$desktop\\$ext\"\n    if (!(Test-Path $folder)) { New-Item $folder -ItemType Directory }\n    Move-Item $_.FullName $folder\n}\n```\n\n### 按日期整理\n```powershell\n# 按月份归档\nGet-ChildItem -Recurse | Where-Object { $_.LastWriteTime -lt (Get-Date).AddDays(-30) }\n```\n\n## 定时任务\n\n- 每天自动执行\n- 保持桌面整洁\n\n---\n*产出日期：2026-03-17*\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\workspace\\knowledge\\16-文件整理自动化.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":38930,"output":313,"cacheRead":36913,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76156,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773761810341}}
