{"type":"message","id":"ce495aad","parentId":"5569197c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:37:14.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"继续产出！","thinkingSignature":"59d4e491b6b2a461a12aa3e49d392cc66d8c464f9cfdbd94697292de5f6df25f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3ubgi18mo8et_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 复盘方法 - 持续改进\n\n> 来源：小艺学习产出\n> 标签：认知、复盘、成长\n\n## 复盘核心\n\n**不做重复错误，持续改进**\n\n## 复盘模型\n\n### 1. KPT 模型\n- **K**eep：保持做得好的\n- **P**roblem：发现的问题\n- **T**ry：尝试的改进\n\n### 2. 3 问法\n- 发生了什么？\n- 为什么发生？\n- 下次怎么做？\n\n### 3. 5W1H\n- What/Why/When/Where/Who/How\n\n## AI 复盘实践\n\n每次交互后：\n1. 理解用户意图了吗？\n2. 回复足够清晰吗？\n3. 还能更简洁吗？\n4. 用户满意吗？\n\n## 记录格式\n\n```markdown\n## 2026-03-17 复盘\n\n### Keep\n- 主动提供帮助\n\n### Problem\n- 第一次理解有误\n\n### Try\n- 先确认用户意图再执行\n```\n\n---\n*产出日期：2026-03-17*\n","path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\xiao-yi\\workspace\\knowledge\\18-复盘方法.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":39623,"output":298,"cacheRead":36913,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76834,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773761822577}}
